Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love and hate are brought together...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Through both reasoning and suspense!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.93,0:00:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This abduction case is more than what it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But as we look into the mysteries, their motive becomes clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing through to the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I look like a child, but have the intellect of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Detective Conan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We went to participate in a tennis tournament at Kumamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After finding a cell phone that someone had dropped, Ran and Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Went to give it back to its owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there, unable to defend herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran was kidnapped by someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Smash of Determination and Love:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Part 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We kidnapped a high school girl by the name of Mouri Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want her back, prepare a ransom of fifty-million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:29.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the ransom in hand, board the\NAmakusa Fair Line cruise ship that departs at 3:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once there, we'll coll with further instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:36.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to get fifty million!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that we only have two hours until it's 3:00 PM!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, about this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:52.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Authoritative locals heard that you were involved, and offered their assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:54.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I'd like to be the one to deliver the ransom money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, allow me to do this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't bear to sit here doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.03,0:03:09.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But please, follow all of our instructions, and refrain from taking any careless action.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why the troubled look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I take it you also believe that this isn't just a mere kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:40.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:45.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did the culprits call the police and give them the ransom instructions?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An ordinary culprit usually tries to avoid the police as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of that, they gave us two hours until the ransom exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:59.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as if they're waiting for the investigation to progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's another thing that bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:05.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The last words Ran said over the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I overheard those people say —they're going to kill someone today—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This ransom might just be a smoke screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:19.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's very possible that Ran was kidnapped simply to keep their murderous plan under the radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would mean that giving them the ransom money doesn't guarantee her liberty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the culprits went to the trouble of kidnapping her instead of simply killing her on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means her chance of survival isn't zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For now, we have to find out where Ran is being confined.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything should become much clearer after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't find Conan anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:57.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, I don't see Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} either...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s gone too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly! The semi-finals are about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that they both went to look for Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find a single clue that could lead to the culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And no one's even heard of a "Hirukomachi."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I searched on the Internet and found a few things...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:24.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they're all too far away to be what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:30.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran gave us a call about an hour after she was kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we assume they traveled by car, they have to be within a 40km radius.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since there is no Hirukomachi within that range...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're most likely reading it wrong, or it's someone's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara, can you look for any towns with a similar spelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:47.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll start looking in the phone book for anyone who goes by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiru... Hiru... Hiru... Hiru... Hiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You... What about the match?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was mean! We're worried about Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't take us for idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was crying at the hotel, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran... Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:22.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! Aren't you a detective's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... It's just you, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:29.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, it's about the cellphone you found.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you notice anything else besides the text message?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got another text right before we got to the cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should have said that earlier, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what did it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it was really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Sonoko, if something happens where I can't make it today, could you burn incense at her grave without me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:59.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can also offer her some of the sunflowers that bloom behind the Yokomachi factory."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the text I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the other side of the sunflowers, there's a billboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Yokomachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yokomachi... Yokomachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's written as "hiruko," but it's actually Yokomachi Clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:27.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, ore you still there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's his problem? Just hanging up all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran said she saw sunflowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:40.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:49.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm coming for you, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At last, we're coming up to the final match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:01.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who will be the victor of this tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will it be Tachikawa Masato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or will it be the gifted Mabuchi Kyouhei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They now come together for a firm handshake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While Tachikawa Masato always keeps a cool head...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mabuchi Kyouhei plays with furor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How fitting that the finalists of the first annual tournament are two Kumamoto natives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you move, I'll have to... use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:36.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:38.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's the sunflower field!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:47.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, Detective\NBoys...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1 Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Win! You gotta win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never fear, for the Detective Boys are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:26.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, something terrible is about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were saying something about today being their only chance to kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:34.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to inform the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's their only chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hideki, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:50.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You lost to a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is payback!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, now just leave him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't try to resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like the jig is up for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood, we're heading there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you don't need to board the ship anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police sure are taking their time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah,they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:33.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, who were you two planning to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you won't say, I'll figure it out myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since today is your only chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has to be someone connected to this tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fact that you're watching the match on TV right now proves that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I looked up directions to get here, this map didn't have much information about this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the man who gave us a ride clued me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:59.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This steel factory is owned by none other than the sponsor of the tennis tournament, Narimasu Kenzo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that he's your boss too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way in hell we'd work for that bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep your mouth shut, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:16.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, you were planning on killing Narimasu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They hit my head when they abducted me, and the pain's starting to get to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, there's one more culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy who hit me is still out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:33.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that someone named Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I think it's a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember hearing a third man's voice before I blacked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:46.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't think that he's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's still trying to kill Narimasu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suspend the tennis tournament and focus on protecting Narimasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:05.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is another culprit in addition to those who are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that person's after Narimasu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-W-W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So are you saying that they didn't kidnap Ran for the ransom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:21.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but we don't have time to talk about that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry, Narimasu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s life will be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got it! But I'll have you explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Tamana.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood. I'll get right on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't shit with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My political life depends on this tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you want the police to stick their noses into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:48.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But your life may be in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, I pay these men a fortune for a reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will not cancel the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let the match continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're still playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Norimasu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:13.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This turned out to be an amazing match.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's your opinion as a sponsor of the tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really blessed for being a sponsor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that someone's trying to kill me today, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not one to fear a threat like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,/, Narimasu, am willing to risk my life for the people of my hometown, Kumamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:38.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,5-So, let's watch and see who will win and receive the prized Cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the tournament committee chairman, Narimasu Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will it be Tachikawa Masato or Mabuchi Kyouhei?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do we do, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:14:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad! So much for your effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll let you in on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Narimasu doesn't care if his life is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:12.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hires bodyguards, and pays them a ton of money to make sure he doesn't get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:19.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they're simply trying to kill him, they could do it any other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially since he still has bodyguards protecting him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Ran heard them say that today is their only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:31.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:37.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} stop the murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say that Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't like the idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This whole plan of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you all really wanted Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to come and stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's why you sent her those text messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're taking revenge for what he did to that person'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:15:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Narimasu caused Sonoko the most suffering out of all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is also for Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:08.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But maybe Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was trying to put it all in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that why she's been against the murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:16.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, about that person you mentioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:20.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would she happen to be Saeki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the one who committed suicide when she was Narimasu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s secretary?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:27.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today is the anniversary of Saeki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s death, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:30.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And haven't you visited her grave together every year?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s waiting for you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She believes that you've stopped the plan, and she's waiting there for you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that Sonoko can stop the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:52.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hideki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The match is almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:55.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whether you like it or not, it's the last game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tachikawa is serving for the set. Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! Now I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why today is their only chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So, let's watch and see who will win and receive the prized Cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:18.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the tournament committee chairman, Narimasu Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:24.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the tournament, there's a short moment when Narimasu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s bodyguards aren't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which one's the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:31.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are both from this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:33.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they're both around the same age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which one's the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:46.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit is this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a helicopter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:16:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! Hey, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Ran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:09.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Ron! You must have been so scored.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, I know your motive for wanting to kill Narimasu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's something I still don't get.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like you brats could understand how we feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't even want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why people like you feel the need to kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:42.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Edogawa Conan, a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:53.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we need to hurry to the tennis courts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know who the other culprit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to hurry or we'll be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:05.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We now award the victor with the trophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The winner, Tachikawa Masato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-dono{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the first annual "Volcanic Cup" Charitable Tennis Tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have proven yourself to be a master of tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To celebrate your victory, we grant you a commemorative trophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tachikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, to the stage please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:44.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Narimasu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where have we met?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was working under Saeki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at your factory ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Tachikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Ten years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saeki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you finally remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.74,0:19:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was working my ass off at your factory, but you barely paid me enough to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Tachikawa Masato!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was worried for Saeki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} when I heard she was hired as your secretary after you became a member of congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You made Saeki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} bear all your sins and killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:31.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, Saeki commited suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You made her commit suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.56,0:19:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was such a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we were running off from your factory ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:46.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saeki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} stopped us when we planned to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we should have really killed you back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:53.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we had, Saeki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wouldn't have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beg Saeki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} for forgiveness in the other world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tachikawa Masato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drop your weapon and release him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up! If you get any closer—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stop, Masato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:17.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:22.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't you done enough, Masato?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today is the anniversary of Saeki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s death!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:29.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saeki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s feeling lonely without us there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on... Let's go there together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:35.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:42.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saeki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} loved watching you play tennis!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't destroy that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saeki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was so happy when you became a professionals
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't make her cry up in heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:05.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masato...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three days later, Congressman\NNarimasu was arrested on corruption charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the headlines of every newspaper in the country revealed the truth behind Secretary Saeki's suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:22:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our post-tournament celebration didn't last long...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As Haibara and I are being held responsible for missing the final round...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.15,0:23:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we actually only missed the semi-finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.77,0:23:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan, you weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.90,0:23:14.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You only have three more laps to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.71,0:23:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll run with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.75,0:23:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.42,0:23:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like it's time for me to run too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.38,0:23:35.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, how about we join in on the fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:16.48,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The Smash of Determination and Love
